column5: Big Cliff, Crappieperchhunter, my step-son Mike and Meely's neighbor Mike for helping out...I couldn't have done it without you...  I hope you enjoyed the hot dogs...
Sorry I couldn't make it up Beano. I was helping you out tho..... Contributing to your old age pension fund!!  Meely
It was a pleasure Beans! And that was the best hot dog I've ever had!
No problem Beansie.  Now that the chores are done we gotta start chasing some carp.  Lotsa them rolling around Carp Point yesterday afternoon
